middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/fc820f31-1450-43ae-a65e-09b7cd08ec18.png\"/> và <img style = \"vertical-align:middle\" src= \"https://asset.moon.vn/new-latex/2026/1/a1905cbc-19c2-43e8-9ef0-47235a00f151.png\"/> song song.\n",
